%% Session phases — Brick Counter Coordinator
%%
%% Route and nav detail: docs/support/application-views.md
%% Storyboard implementation: feature/00-shipped/storyboard-ui/
%%
%% Phases apply after a session is created (Home → New session). Production will
%% persist phase on a coordinator server; storyboard simulates phase in memory.

stateDiagram-v2
    direction LR

    [*] --> importing: Create session
    importing --> counting: Confirm part-out
    counting --> reconciling: Compare with Part-Out List
    reconciling --> organizing: Declare ready to organize
    organizing --> updating_inventory: Declare ready to import
    organizing --> reconciling: Return to reconciling
    organizing --> counting: Back to counting
    reconciling --> counting: Back to counting
    updating_inventory --> organizing: Back to organizing
    updating_inventory --> reconciling: Back to reconciling
    updating_inventory --> counting: Back to counting
    updating_inventory --> closed: Mark session complete
    closed --> [*]

    note right of importing
        Part-out import
        /session/:id/import
        SessionNav hidden
    end note

    note right of counting
        Lot entry (default landing)
        /session/:id/lot
        SessionNav: Home, Lot, Lots, Reconcile, Cups
    end note

    note right of reconciling
        Reconciliation
        /session/:id/reconciliation
        Resolve all rows, then organize
        Cups nav available
    end note

    note right of organizing
        List lots (organizer mode)
        /session/:id/lots?mode=organizer
        Pick lists; Reconcile nav still visible
        Return to reconciling keeps organizer progress
    end note

    note right of updating_inventory
        Reconciliation (same view, later chapter)
        /session/:id/reconciliation
        Export XML, then complete session
        Cups nav hidden
    end note

    note right of closed
        Session routes redirect to Home (/)
    end note
